    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years. You\u2019ll love how smoothly it handles on the road! It\u2019s clean, reliable, and ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
