    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound F87 M2 featuring the N55 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six. This unit delivers a broad torque band and remains thermally efficient thanks to its robust cooling package. The 7-speed M Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) provides crisp, rev-matched downshifts, while the Active M Differential ensures optimal torque vectoring across the rear axle. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with M-specific suspension geometry and aluminum control arms. Recent preventative maintenance includes a drive belt replacement and a comprehensive fluid service. This is a high-performance athlete with a focused cockpit and a clean mechanical bill of health.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
